org.midica.file

Interface IParser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MidicaPLParser, MidiParser, SequenceParser, SoundfontParser

    public interface IParser

    This interface can be implemented by parser classes which can parse an input file.

    It’s implemented by the following classes:

    • SoundfontParser – loads a soundfont file (.sf2)
    • SequenceParser – parses a MIDI stream using one of the following sub classes:
      • MidiParser – parses the stream from a MIDI file (.mid)
      • MidicaPLParser – parses the stream from a MidicaPL file (.midica)
